<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>47-1303.03</num>
  <heading>Tax deed.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The Mayor shall issue a deed for the bid off property sold pursuant to § <cite path="§47-1303.02">47-1303.02</cite> to the person whose offer the Mayor accepts.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The deed shall be prima facie evidence of a good and perfect title in fee simple to the bid off property.</text>
  </para>
